    ClosingAwareWebDriverWrapper

    public class WebDriverWrapper
extends org.openqa.selenium.support.events.EventFiringWebDriver
implements org.openqa.selenium.HasCapabilities, io.appium.java_client.MobileDriver, io.appium.java_client.android.AndroidDeviceActionShortcuts, io.appium.java_client.android.HasNetworkConnection, io.appium.java_client.android.PushesFiles, io.appium.java_client.android.StartsActivity, io.appium.java_client.FindsByAndroidUIAutomator, io.appium.java_client.ios.IOSDeviceActionShortcuts, io.appium.java_client.FindsByIosUIAutomation, org.openqa.selenium.internal.HasIdentity
    This class is a "simple" extension of Selenium's EventFiringWebDriver that additionally implements several useful interfaces.
